text: Ne obubii bubulao khwinywe tawe nimulekha Abakhasi bamushili okhuba ninabo nohomba bamushili okhubahelesia omurungo kwabu. Halali mubahelesie shiokhubahotselesia, uli nende obunyali shingala anyalilwa ne wobunyakhani shingala anyalilwa, eshihotselesio okhulondokhana shinga emilukha chiboola, ni obwatoto khubakholi bamalayi
